name: Biome control
description: Toggle who can change the island biome.

name: Biome Island limitation
description: Toggle requirement for players to be on their island to change biome.

name: Magic Generator
description: Toggle to enable or disable all Magic Generators on the whole island.

name: Magic Generator Permissions
description: Select who can activate and deactivate generators.

name: Visit protection
description: Toggle if island can be visited by anyone.

name: Receive Visiting Messages
description: Toggle if members should receive a message if someone visits their island.
